that coupled stellar-tidal evolution of pre-main sequence\nbinary stars removes at least one close-in CBP in $87\\%$ of multi-planet\ncircumbinary systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 18:19:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
