ity matrices of 33432 small molecules\nobtained at Hartree-Fock and 2-nd order Moller-Plesset theory levels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 21:16:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-12"}
